Reclusa::

She didn't like the idea of having to leave her body behind. "Any set
back to this plan?  Sure, it will fool the maximals, but do we have a
maximal pod handy or will we have to build one? And, if I should need
it, how in the Pit will I prove I'm on our side and not the maxicreeps
should I get into a situation. Not every bot on this ship is going to
know of this little coo except you and Hydras."  Then she smiled,
"However, I must admit, you are a genius. Pure genius to have thought
of such a way to carry out this plan. No wonder Hydras favors you so
highly." she said with a seductive smile.
